# Testing rules

- Add regression tests before risky refactors.
- For backend critical flows, prefer API/integration tests plus focused unit tests.
- Mock external providers: Stripe, PayPal, DPD, GLS, Packeta.
- Payment webhook tests must check idempotency.
- Order creation tests must verify totals, items, user, delivery metadata, and payment metadata.
- Delivery tests must verify provider-specific edge cases.
- Do not remove tests unless the behavior was intentionally removed and documented.